  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can see through fog and mist without penalty as long as there is enough light to allow you to see normal.</p>\n<p>At 7th level, you can use any calm pool of water at least 1 foot in diameter as a scrying device, as if using the @Compendium[pf1.spells.g66w32kdup1f43bp]{Scrying} spell.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, this functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.glt6uk3n6g6l2p6l]{Scrying, Greater}.</p>\n<p>You can use the scrying abilities for a number of rounds per day equal to your oracle level, but these rounds do not need to be consecutive.</p>"
